			<h3>How does it work?</h3>
	    
			<ol>
				<li>Define - Define each test case in plain english. (i.e. Test a user can purchase a widget).</li>
				<li>Review - Outpost writes your tests and provides a video.</li>
				<li>Test - Run the tests when needed or on a recurring schedule. Just log in to your dashboard and tell us when you want to run your tests. We'll take it from there and notify you when the report is ready.</li>
				<li>Reports - When you receive your report you'll see status for each test case. In the event a test fails one of the Outpost team members manually reviews the failure to determine the cause and include a detailed note.</li>
			</ol>
		</div>
